Visual tone: {{ mood_map.get(app_domain, mood_map["default"]) }}.

Colour palette: Use a {% if tech_profile.primary_platform == "mobile" %}mobile-first{% else %}desktop-optimised{% endif %} layout.
Reserve red exclusively for destructive actions and error states.
Reserve green exclusively for success states and confirmations.

Typography: Use a system font stack for body text (performance-first).
{% if app_domain in ["saas", "finance", "productivity"] %}
Use a monospace font for all data values, IDs, and numeric fields.
{% endif %}

Interaction style: All primary CTAs must have a visible loading state.
Form inputs must show inline validation — do not use alert() dialogs.
{% if tech_profile.primary_platform in ["mobile", "both"] %}
All tap targets must be minimum 44×44px. Bottom navigation required.
{% endif %}
